    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a robot with time-manipulating abilities. Travel to places you’ve never been by independently shifting back in time along the X and Y axes. But beware of pockets of corrupted space-time, and remember, tracking your positions through time consumes significant memory—without it, you won’t be able to function.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manipulate Space Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/bae4d1a859293135735c6667834d020f.poster.avif?t=1733933487\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/bae4d1a859293135735c6667834d020f.webm?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/bae4d1a859293135735c6667834d020f.mp4?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate puzzles keeping track of where you have been to reach places you could not reach before!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware of Corrupted Space Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/df3fed0f2a5e35d4ee5a010a42ff5648.poster.avif?t=1733933487\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/df3fed0f2a5e35d4ee5a010a42ff5648.webm?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/df3fed0f2a5e35d4ee5a010a42ff5648.mp4?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The straightest path is not always possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Limited Memory Capacity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/839e42ffc16c45e68ed43da3f21778a4.poster.avif?t=1733933487\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/839e42ffc16c45e68ed43da3f21778a4.webm?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/839e42ffc16c45e68ed43da3f21778a4.mp4?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep track of your memory available or you will over heat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/ea26b90f9c4faf659c3445b0fd3186ef.poster.avif?t=1733933487\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/ea26b90f9c4faf659c3445b0fd3186ef.webm?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127120/extras/ea26b90f9c4faf659c3445b0fd3186ef.mp4?t=1733933487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make levels to share your creativity with others so we can all enjoy more puzzles together!</p>",
